<item>
            <title>[LU-18080] conf-sanity test_32a: replace_nids t32fs-OST0000 failed on el9.4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18080</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/04f76975-23c6-4c44-ad1d-955f9008a6f1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/04f76975-23c6-4c44-ad1d-955f9008a6f1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_32a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== conf-sanity testing /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/disk2_12-ldiskfs.tar.bz2 upgrade ==
Lustre: t32fs-MDT0000-osd: enabled &apos;large_dir&apos; feature on device /dev/loop0
Lustre: 243660:0:(scrub.c:190:scrub_file_load()) t32fs-MDT0000: reset scrub OI count for format change (LU-16655)
LDISKFS-fs error (device loop0): osd_iget2:500: inode #197: comm OI_scrub: unexpected EA_INODE flag
Aborting journal on device loop0-8.
LustreError: 243663:0:(osd_handler.c:1867:osd_trans_commit_cb()) transaction @0xffff90c8861a0c00 commit error: 2
LDISKFS-fs (loop0): Remounting filesystem read-only
LustreError: 243666:0:(scrub.c:243:scrub_file_store()) t32fs-MDT0000: store scrub file: rc = -30
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4558&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4558&lt;/a&gt; - 6.8.0-35-generic&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4558&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4558&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-427.24.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has failed repeatedly with el9.4 servers both before and after the el9.4 server patch series landed:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
conf-sanity test_32a - replace_nids t32fs-OST0000 10.240.22.222@tcp failed&lt;/p&gt;</description>
